  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the results of foam treatment of varicose veins (foam
      sclerotherapy) in patients who wear compression bandages for 24 hours or 5 days after
      treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
