  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Proven truncal venous incompetence (of &gt;1 second duration) on venous duplex scanning.
             (Great saphenous vein (GSV), small saphenous vein (SSV), anterior accessory thigh vein
             (AATV) or other major tributary).

          -  Agreed preference for foam sclerotherapy treatment.

          -  Signed consent form agreeing to be part of the trial.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Total deep venous reflux.

          -  Known allergy to liquid sclerosant.

          -  Pregnancy or breast feeding.

          -  Arterial disease.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
